  TSplus provides Multiple Sessions, Load Balancing, Universal Printer,
  Seamless Remote Application, Application Control, Secure RDP and much
  more without having to implement 2003/2008/2012 TSE or Citrix.

  TSplus is the most cost-effective and easy-to-use alternative to Windows
  Terminal Server (TSE) and Citrix for computers and servers with XP,
  Windows 7, Windows 8, SBS, Windows Server 2003, Windows Server 2008 and
  Windows Server 2012.

  With TSplus you will instantly Web-Enable any of your Windows
  application. Using Java or HTML5 connection client, your Mobile users
  will start application from any devices (iPhone, IPAD, Galaxy, MAC...).
  TSplus gives the ability to run legacy applications inside the web
  browser without the need to rewrite them for the specific device.

  TSplus Seamless and RemoteApp client provides fast, efficient access -
  even over high-latency dial-up lines and Internet connections. From
  TSplus Gateway Portal you will transform Windows desktops and apps into
  Windows-as-a-Service clouds.

  TSplus is completely transparent to your users. Remote applications look
  and feel exactly the same way as natively-running applications.
  Therefore, you save time and training costs.

  TSplus is outstanding to publish Windows applications over Internet
  hosted on XP, W7 or W8. TSplus is a fast, simple and cost-less solution
  that eliminates the complexity of alternatives such as Windows TSE or
  Citrix.

  As a leader in mobile work style solutions, flexible ways of working,
  TSplus empowers executives to work, meet and collaborate anywhere inside
  or outside the organization, on any of the latest devices, as easily as
  they would in their own office - simply and securely.
